TITLE**: CS:S Map - fy_getxtexture
AUTHOR**: Grae

WEBSITE: http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/228156

FILENAME: /maps/fy_getxtexture.bsp,/maps/fy_getxtexture.txt,/materials/credits.vmt
FILESIZE: 1,234,291 bytes (1.17 MB)
DATE RELEASED: 14 August 2007 

CREDITS**: This map was requested by Getxclean for the Elite Force gaming community (www.eliteforce.clanservers.com) for their 24/7 GunGame server.

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS**: Extract all contents of the .zip file directly into your "\Program Files\Steam\SteamApps\YOURNAMEHERE\counter-strike source\cstrike\" folder.

DESCRIPTION**: A(nother) developer texture map. Like the orange and gray maps? This is for you. Made for the Elite Force gaming community (www.eliteforce.clanservers.com).
***They asked me to make a small, 6v6/8v8 map, and that's what this is; it's small, and guarantees fast rounds, and heavy body pileups.***
It's a relatively small map but there's a lot of cover, and still plenty of smaller open spaces. It's meant for GunGame, and plays best as such.

COMMENTS: No third-party/third-person testing was done before the release of this map. If you have any problems, tell me on my FPSBanana page ("WEBSITE"), the EF forums (URL above), or e-mail me. Copyright 2007 Grae Matter Studios some rights reserved.

**Required items: Counter-Strike: Source
